<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 14:38:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>迈克尔·塞勒的比特币飞轮存在优先股问题</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-18/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-flywheel-has-a-preferred-stock-problem</link><description>证券的暴跌实际上关闭了Strategy融资机制的一个关键环节。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixzm2y8U5WAM/v7/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-18/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-flywheel-has-a-preferred-stock-problem</guid></item><item><title>策略股、利率担忧导致比特币回落至 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/bitcoin-btc-slides-toward-60-000-as-saylor-s-strategy-funding-model-unravels</link><description>比特币延续跌势，重返 60,000 美元水平。股价下跌的原因是对Strategy Inc.融资机制瓦解的担忧日益加剧，以及对加息的担忧抑制了对高风险资产的需求。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_t_RB3YAu3g/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 17:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/bitcoin-btc-slides-toward-60-000-as-saylor-s-strategy-funding-model-unravels</guid></item><item><title>股价暴跌 90% 后加密货币金库梦想破灭</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/the-crypto-treasury-dream-unravels-after-a-90-stock-plunge</link><description>成立一家上市公司购买加密货币的商业模式正在崩溃。结果，在极其不友好的市场背景下，那些排队通过空白支票公司这样做的人面临着来自投资者的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iXYhaoOKrSL0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/the-crypto-treasury-dream-unravels-after-a-90-stock-plunge</guid></item><item><title>新加坡将加密货币公司 Bybit 添加到投资者警报名单中</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/singapore-adds-crypto-firm-bybit-to-its-investor-alert-list</link><description>新加坡金融管理局周三将 Bybit Fintech Ltd. 添加到投资者警报名单中，以加强对未经许可的加密货币交易所的审查。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1ncZrHTv82o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 09:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-18/singapore-adds-crypto-firm-bybit-to-its-investor-alert-list</guid></item><item><title>日夜交易：华尔街的文化变革</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-17/wall-street-avanza-hacia-mercados-24-7-por-presion-cripto</link><description>&lt;p&gt;传统金融实体开始评估各种资产不间断交易的模型，这种方式多年来一直在彻底改变加密货币领域的时间表。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyQz9bOauOsQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 17:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-17/wall-street-avanza-hacia-mercados-24-7-por-presion-cripto</guid></item></channel></rss>